Subject: categories: logics for model checking
Date: Tue, 2 Sep 2008 10:24:13 -0400
From: "Wojtowicz, Ralph" <wojtowicz@metsci.com>
To: <categories@mta.ca>
Sender: cat-dist@mta.ca
