Dear all,

Here is a bit of additional information about the full professor
position at Universit=E9 de Savoie I advertised in July (full
message below).

The schedule for 'qualification' is available here

=
http://www.education.gouv.fr/personnel/enseignant_superieur/enseignant_che=
rcheur/calendrier_qualification.htm=20
